RT @NYDailyNews: A 32-year-old boxer was fatally shot on a return visit home to Staten Island early Sunday.

RT @NYDailyNews: Olivia de Havilland, who played the sweetest character in "Gone With the Wind," has died in Paris. She was 104.

She played the saintly Melanie Wilkes in the 1939 epic film — setting the bar for pure-hearted nobility that few actresses reach again.
